dified like that. <br /><br />Interestingly enough, Doctor Who plays without a hitch even with those odd problems.", "objectType": "comment"}, "updated": "2013-11-03T23:50:20.332Z", "actor": {"url": "https://plus.google.com/100687763722533869658", "image": {"url": "https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/-9ao4QUtSct0/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAK2Q/B_aFdM62MLU/photo.jpg?sz=50"}, "displayName": "Don Takahashi", "id": "100687763722533869658"}, "verb": "post", "etag": "\"Mwea3qudNDf-hWWlPWi3n-YrU1Q/N5AcAC0bWmA25zNxNENQvCIEYf8\"", "published": "2013-11-03T23:50:20.332Z", "id": "z12huz5qmsakfnpxa04cf51gkzuqfzm5mkg0k.1383522620332126", "selfLink": "https://www.googleapis.com/plus/v1/comments/z12huz5qmsakfnpxa04cf51gkzuqfzm5mkg0k#1383522620332126"}, {"inReplyTo": [{"url": "https://plus.google.com/100687763722533869658/posts/Ut34xx3SQfU", "id": "z12huz5qmsakfnpxa04cf51gkzuqfzm5mkg0k"}], "kind": "plus#comment", "plusoners": {"totalItems": 0}, "object": {"content": "Pogoplug v4mobile plus archlinux the ppv4 is 18 bucks shipped on amazon", "objectType": "comment"}, "updated": "2013-11-04T05:24:30.658Z", "actor": {"url": "https://plus.google.com/102662434857820698209", "image": {"url": "https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/-lJwxdyXSs1g/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAEDU/DtkUBFViC5k/photo.jpg?sz=50"}, "displayName": "Daniel Bert Strand", "id": "102662434857820698209"}, "verb": "post", "etag": "\"Mwea3qudNDf-hWWlPWi3n-YrU1Q/YiAaANo0UtlcyrD3CwLQnhLt1FE\"", "published": "2013-11-04T05:24:30.658Z", "id": "z12huz5qmsakfnpxa04cf51gkzuqfzm5mkg0k.1383542670658741", "selfLink": "https://www.googleapis.com/plus/v1/comments/z12huz5qmsakfnpxa04cf51gkzuqfzm5mkg0k#1383542670658741"}, {"inReplyTo": [{"url": "https://plus.google.com/100687763722533869658/posts/Ut34xx3SQfU", "id": "z12huz5qmsakfnpxa04cf51gkzuqfzm5mkg0k"}], "kind": "plus#comment", "plusoners": {"totalItems": 1}, "object": {"content": "<span class=\"proflinkWrapper\"><span class=\"proflinkPrefix\">+</span><a href=\"https://plus.google.com/100687763722533869658\" class=\"proflink\" oid=\"100687763722533869658\">Don Takahashi</a></span>\u00a0What OS are you running?<br />Raspbian ran fine from boot on the RCA video XBMC has always worked great with standard def.\u00a0<br />Whats better is it automatically adjusts when your using HDMI, no config/settings to adjust.", "objectType": "comment"}, "updated": "2013-11-04T13:17:15.097Z", "actor": {"url": "https://plus.google.com/107077327095876586707", "image": {"url": "https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/-TuryzRnx50w/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAQdI/rYMIB_KW-yY/photo.jpg?sz=50"}, "displayName": "Thew Raslletem", "id": "107077327095876586707"}, "verb": "post", "etag": "\"Mwea3qudNDf-hWWlPWi3n-YrU1Q/CfdT-eODNZVaQ0Vvs56YIty0Fdc\"", "published": "2013-11-04T13:17:15.097Z", "id": "z12huz5qmsakfnpxa04cf51gkzuqfzm5mkg0k.1383571035097572", "selfLink": "https://www.googleapis.com/plus/v1/comments/z12huz5qmsakfnpxa04cf51gkzuqfzm5mkg0k#1383571035097572"}, {"inReplyTo": [{"url": "https://plus.google.com/100687763722533869658/posts/Ut34xx3SQfU", "id": "z12huz5qmsakfnpxa04cf51gkzuqfzm5mkg0k"}], "kind": "plus#comment", "plusoners": {"totalItems": 0}, "object": {"content": "<span class=\"proflinkWrapper\"><span class=\"proflinkPrefix\">+</span><a href=\"https://plus.google.com/107077327095876586707\" class=\"proflink\" oid=\"107077327095876586707\">Thew Raslletem</a></span>\u00a0Raspbian via NOOBS. Because apparently NOOBS installs everything with &quot;force-hdmi=1&quot;. Kinda dumb, but that&#39;s how it seems to be.", "objectType": "comment"}, "updated": "2013-11-04T15:01:51.121Z", "actor": {"url": "https://plus.google.com/100687763722533869658", "image": {"url": "https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/-9ao4QUtSct0/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAK2Q/B_aFdM62MLU/photo.jpg?sz=50"}, "displayName": "Don Takahashi", "id": "100687763722533869658"}, "verb": "post", "etag": "\"Mwea3qudNDf-hWWlPWi3n-YrU1Q/UbKupmo3xvBZGGqzuZ97nSH_ajU\"", "published": "2013-11-04T15:01:51.121Z", "id": "z12huz5qmsakfnpxa04cf51gkzuqfzm5mkg0k.1383577311121126", "selfLink": "https://www.googleapis.com/plus/v1/comments/z12huz5qmsakfnpxa04cf51gkzuqfzm5mkg0k#1383577311121126"}, {"inReplyTo": [{"url": "https://plus.google.com/100687763722533869658/posts/Ut34xx3SQfU", "id": "z12huz5qmsakfnpxa04cf51gkzuqfzm5mkg0k"}], "kind": "plus#comment", "plusoners": {"totalItems": 0}, "object": {"content": "Well then, the best part of linux is having to know how things work, because you never know how they will be packaged.", "objectType": "comment"}, "updated": "2013-11-04T15:09:43.397Z", "actor": {"url": "https://plus.google.com/107077327095876586707", "image": {"url": "https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/-TuryzRnx50w/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAQdI/rYMIB_KW-yY/photo.jpg?sz=50"}, "displayName": "Thew Raslletem", "id": "107077327095876586707"}, "verb": "post", "etag": "\"Mwea3qudNDf-hWWlPWi3n-YrU1Q/J5g4pLtxHAquqqMlR2oy2--nv4U\"", "published": "2013-11-04T15:09:43.397Z", "id": "z12huz5qmsakfnpxa04cf51gkzuqfzm5mkg0k.1383577783397572", "selfLink": "https://www.googleapis.com/plus/v1/comments/z12huz5qmsakfnpxa04cf51gkzuqfzm5mkg0k#1383577783397572"}, {"inReplyTo": [{"url": "https://plus.google.com/100687763722533869658/posts/Ut34xx3SQfU", "id": "z12huz5qmsakfnpxa04cf51gkzuqfzm5mkg0k"}], "kind": "plus#comment", "plusoners": {"totalItems": 0}, "object": {"content": "I&#39;m not <i>exactly</i> sure if a day of troubleshooting, wondering if it was my SD card or my power or my connection to the TV was the problem, was exactly productive. And automatically forcing an unnecessary option was completely counterintuitive. The best part of any OS is it working.", "objectType": "comment"}, "updated": "2013-11-04T15:42:42.484Z", "actor": {"url": "https://plus.google.com/100687763722533869658", "image": {"url": "https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/-9ao4QUtSct0/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAK2Q/B_aFdM62MLU/photo.jpg?sz=50"}, "displayName": "Don Takahashi", "id": "100687763722533869658"}, "verb": "post", "etag": "\"Mwea3qudNDf-hWWlPWi3n-YrU1Q/Pa_LYt3Jk4AEHu1fZYG6CXv7vhU\"", "published": "2013-11-04T15:42:42.484Z", "id": "z12huz5qmsakfnpxa04cf51gkzuqfzm5mkg0k.1383579762484126", "selfLink": "https://www.googleapis.com/plus/v1/comments/z12huz5qmsakfnpxa04cf51gkzuqfzm5mkg0k#1383579762484126"}], "kind": "plus#commentFeed", "etag": "\"Mwea3qudNDf-hWWlPWi3n-YrU1Q/uKhkYfPWE5UkzcvOs3C2bKLyFvs\"", "title": "Google+ List of Comments for an Activity"}]